content:
Bring the power of conversational AI to your business with Einstein Copilot. 

Einstein Copilot features are released as often as monthly, and there’s much more to come in Summer ’24.

In July's release, you can give feedback on Copilot responses, see different object records in searches, and clear your Copilot history to start a new session.

In June’s release, Einstein Copilot end users can clear Einstein Copilot feed history and receive a confirmation request before a copilot makes changes in your org.
title: Einstein Copilot Summer '24 Release Notes
